
<h3>UPGRADE: Ability to Copy Questions and Answers from Dev to Live</h3>
<p>It is our intention to extend the Synchronisation facility to include Questions and Answers. Users will have the ability to select multiple steps and documents and create a migration which can be actioned immediately or saved to execute at a later date.</p>
<br />
<h3>UPGRADE: New Global Milestone Status and Status Tracking</h3>
<p>We are extending the status capture modude to include a global milestone status. This new milestone status can be set within the normal Smartflow Status tab within GadjIT or Excel.</p>
<p>All changes to Smartflow status and the global Milestone Status are now tracked within the table Usr_ORSF_MT_Status_History. This table will contain a full breakdown of all status changes including dates and times.</p>
<br />
