</p>
<h3>ISSUE: Upgrading Smartflow Steps</h3>
<p>At the moment, if we upgrade the Smartflow step, each Smartflow has to be entered (within GadjIT) to be upgraded.</p>
<h4>SOLUTION: Auto Update All Steps</h4>
<p>Orchard Rock and Admin Users will have the ability to update all Smartflows to the latest version with one click. Dev and Live systems will still be independent so if both systems require an upgrade then the user will have to activate both separately.</p>
